    <p>In User Navigation, click the <strong>Observing </strong>link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="paste-pairing-code" data-step-uuid="299eca85-8bfe-43ff-a98b-21113fcbb17c">
    <h2 id="paste-pairing-code" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Student</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/207/105/original/6a32d82c-52d6-48fb-a5a7-028435ea7b61.png" srcset="" alt="Add Student" height="197" width="273">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_dfa0b09e-6f5d-49d7-bd69-e247491be011" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Type the pairing code in the <strong>Student Pairing Code</strong> field [1] and click the <strong>Add Student</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

